<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM6.5">
<l>katiroḷi tīpaṅ kalacamu ṭaṉēntic</l>
<l>catiriḷa maṅkaiyar tāmvan tetirkoḷḷa</l>
<l>maturaiyār maṉṉa ṉaṭinilai toṭṭeṅku</l>
<l>matirap pukutak kaṉāk kaṇṭēṉ tōḻīnāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O friend! I dreamt that the king of the people of Mathurā</l>
<l>entered [the wedding hall] wearing sandals, so that [the earth] shook,</l>
<l>as the beautiful young women came and received [Him]</l>
<l>holding lamps shining [like] the sun along with pots of consecrated water.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
